We just returned from a pre-cruise stay in Rome at the Cicerone Hotel.	However, that would not stop me from staying here again as I did not go to Rome to stay in my room.	Just enjoy Rome and don't expect a friendly hotel staff if you stay here.	For what we paid to stay here, we did not recieve good value for our money.	I walked and walked every day and it was really comfortable to stay in Cicerone to reach all those places in a very short time.	I would stay there again and I would recommend it to my friends.